Package com.blackrook.redis.event

Interface RedisSubscriptionListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RedisSubscriptionAdapter, RedisSubscriptionDebugListener
    public interface RedisSubscriptionListener
    A listener class that listens on fired events from a Redis channel subscription.

    Matthew Tropiano
